                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/5559" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">MSL-0072</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8658 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“混”出活力，“改”出成效：天津建材的混改之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">&quot;Mix&quot; brings vitality and &quot;reform&quot; brings effect: the road of Tianjin Building Materials mix and change </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">季柯辛，韩玉琪，崔敏杰（通讯作者），张璐，耿燕男</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">内蒙古工业大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">天津建材集团（控股）有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">建筑、建材业与房地产业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">14 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">混合所有制改革；并购；天津建材；北京金隅；2021百优案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">mixed ownership reform; mergers and acquisitions; Tianjin Building Materials; BBMG</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">天津建材集团（控股）有限公司（以下简称“天津建材”）在2017年接到混改任务后，在董事长胡景山的带领下，一路“披荆斩棘”，历经混改路径、层面及战略投资者的选择、清理僵尸企业、争取政策支持，最终顺利“被并购”实现在集团层面的“混”，成功打响天津国企混改第一枪。随后，天津建材积极落实战略合作构想，全面对接战略投资者北京金隅集团股份有限公司（以下简称“金隅”）的组织架构和治理体系，完成了关键的“改”。混改后的天津建材轻装上阵，不断焕发新的生机。本案例旨在以并购理论帮助学生理解混改动机、合作伙伴选择、并购风险以及并购整合等关键内容，为其他国企混改和弱势企业通过并购寻求发展提供理论参考。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Tianjin Building Materials group (holding) co., LTD. (hereinafter referred to as the &quot;Tianjin Building Materials&quot;) in 2017 after receiving mixed change task, under the guidance of chairman Hu Jingshan, all the way through the thorns, after the path and level of mixed reform and the choice of strategic investors, clean up zombie enterprises, and strive for policy support, finally &quot;be merged&quot; to achieve the &quot;mix&quot; at the group level, successfully launched the first shot of mixed reform of state-owned enterprises in Tianjin. After that, Tianjin Building Materials actively implemented the strategic cooperation concept, comprehensively connected with the organizational structure and governance system of strategic investor BBMG Group Co., Ltd. (hereinafter referred to as &quot;BBMG&quot;), and completed the key &quot;reform&quot;. After the mixed reform, Tianjin Building Materials began to carry on light, constantly glowing with new vitality. This case aims to help students understand the motivation of mixed-use reform, partner selection, M&amp;A risk, M&amp;A integration and other key contents, and provide theoretical reference for other state-owned mixed-use reform and weak enterprises to seek development through M&amp;A.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2020</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《企业并购与重组》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">目标企业选择 并购后整合</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021-10</td>
                            </tr>
